                <h1>Bernie Sanders calls for a ‘political revolution’ at campaign rally at UNC</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/c492f214-f21a-463d-8b78-0980a298d201.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
